div.div: Its a world where a magical tree grows from the back of a swordsman, a mute girl is turned into a living weapon by her mother, a frost dragon roams the skies seeking vengeance, and beings with godlike powers clash for the balance of nature. In the middle of it all is Bira, an orphaned boy, happily spending his days fishing inside a secluded forest. Then he meets Tanyu, a former general on a quest to find his childhood love. Together, they journey into an enchanted landscape unlike any other. (Source: Tapas)

When the disaster called "Portal Impact" ended it left Park Hyun-So to pick up the pieces after his parents' death and his younger brother was left in a deep coma. Years later after suffering hardships and massively in debt due to his brother's hospital bills, Hyun-Soo meets Chung-Yeong, a martial artist from another world! Chung-Yeong, a murim martial master who had been astral projecting could not return to his body, when a portal appeared and sucked him in, taking him to modern Korea. After months not being able to interact with anyone Chung-Yeong out of boredom takes on Hyun-Soo as his student and begins to teach him martial arts
